    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a concours-level 2018 BMW M2 LCI, a pinnacle of longitudinal rear-wheel-drive engineering. This specimen is powered by the N55 3.0L inline-six utilizing a twin-scroll turbocharger and Valvetronic variable valve timing, delivering a flat torque curve and immediate throttle response. It features the 7-speed M Double Clutch Transmission (DCT) with Drivelogic for seamless, millisecond gear changes and an Active M Differential that provides electronically controlled multi-plate limited-slip functionality. The chassis remains factory-spec with aluminum-intensive suspension components to minimize unsprung weight, ensuring surgical turn-in precision. The exterior retains its factory depth with no discernible road rash, while the interior is devoid of any bolster compression or leather fatigue. A meticulously documented service history confirms this vehicle has been maintained to the highest mechanical standards.",
      "price": 48500.0,
