      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies the most discerning collector's standards. This car is in pristine condition, featuring a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like factory finish protected by a multi-layer ceramic coating. There are no stone chips, swirl marks, or imperfections to be found. The interior is equally immaculate, retaining its original 'new car' scent; the premium leather surfaces are supple without a hint of bolster wear, and every electronic component functions exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by master technicians at authorized dealerships. Always garaged in a climate-controlled environment and never driven in inclement weather, this car comes with a complete portfolio of service records, original window sticker, and all spare keys. It is, quite simply, the finest example of its kind available on the market today.",
